window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>What's a Party without the Mixed Nuts?</p> <p>When cryptid chasers Bobbie and Grayson head to a friend's prepper compound for a Halloween party, all bets are off about who the real freak is—even when the masks come off. </p> <p>Grayson is acting strangely out of character. Bobbie's on the hunt for family jewels. Garth and his friends put the Trailer Park Boys to shame. And Earl? He's just being Earl. And quite frankly, that's enough. </p> <p>Full moons. Lord Baldemort. Deadly legume gas. On Halloween, nothing is as it seems. And before the night is through, somebody will have to battle The Great Bumpkin. I mean, what else would you expect? This is Florida, after all. </p> <p>Love<i> The X Files? Stranger Things? Psych?</i> This hilarious, fast-paced paranormal series is for you! Just like this short adventure, each Freaky Florida Investigation is loaded with unique plots and twists and turns you'll never see coming, this humorous take on the supernatural is the smart, addictive, hilarious escape you've been yearning for. Perfect for fans of Brian Yansky, Jack Bodett, Ward Parker, D.M. Guay, and Steve Higgs.</p>"; 
